strings.Value: "People are so busy with pointless worldly vanity... They'd be better off spending their short lives accepting the end with dignity!"
[laughs] "I think, most honorable Harrim, that your dreams of death are like a child, dreaming of becoming an adult and having candy before dinner. Sweet, silly hopes — that pass with time."
